12-14T15:43:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>不如買直立式鋼琴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無太多錢呀嘛<br />\n同埋想慳下位<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n二手is ok<br />\n學琴唔係太建議用數碼(仲要自學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n去上成人鋼琴睇下係咪真係有興趣先"},{"pid":"34165372274e55add51d10a5541b3268ed96a96c","tid":39528,"uid":46200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T15:44:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新手想買部數碼鋼琴自學<br />\nyamaha p115<br />\nroland fp30<br />\nkorg b1<br />\nkorg lp380<br />\ncasio es100<br />\n邊部會好啲?<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者有冇其他選擇?<br />\n筆直應該都係五六千左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n用緊p115<br />\n今年二月買 四千九百幾<br />\n手感同真琴冇得比 差太多<br />\n<br />\n不過我都係新手<br />\n我諗未學夠兩三年 部電琴都夠做<br />\n<br />\nBTW 提醒一句 自學冇好下場<br />\n本來我諗住自己真係掂<br />\n忽忽地咁自學左半年<br />\n最終都係揾左個老師學<br />\n學左先發覺基本功方面差好遠<br />\n<br />\n有閒錢就揾老師啦<br />\n部琴買番嚟 畢竟係新手<br />\n一星期揾一日出去租琴房摸下真琴熟悉下就得"},{"pid":"fa9dba0ca1652c301b42dbdc2ed84e81bf868f43","tid":39528,"uid":2959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T15:48:11.000Z","msg":"琴行租琴練會唔會好啲"},{"pid":"fd5e6a05b5b4482a07493d05d009ec09a3f6d528","tid":39528,"uid":27583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T16:11:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>不如買直立式鋼琴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無太多錢呀嘛<br />\n同埋想慳下位<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n二手is ok<br />\n學琴唔係太建議用數碼(仲要自學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n去上成人鋼琴睇下係咪真係有興趣先</blockquote><br />\n重點係空間問題<br />\n屋企人唔比放廳<br />\n同埋又唔係好想嘈到人<br />\n可以插耳筒<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔該巴打先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05bfcdfb08458e768c6e0ea12fc81d182349c0da","tid":39528,"uid":27583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T16:14:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>新手想買部數碼鋼琴自學<br />\nyamaha p115<br />\nroland fp30<br />\nkorg b1<br />\nkorg lp380<br />\ncasio es100<br />\n邊部會好啲?<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者有冇其他選擇?<br />\n筆直應該都係五六千左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n用緊p115<br />\n今年二月買 四千九百幾<br />\n手感同真琴冇得比 差太多<br />\n<br />\n不過我都係新手<br />\n我諗未學夠兩三年 部電琴都夠做<br />\n<br />\nBTW 提醒一句 自學冇好下場<br />\n本來我諗住自己真係掂<br />\n忽忽地咁自學左半年<br />\n最終都係揾左個老師學<br />\n學左先發覺基本功方面差好遠<br />\n<br />\n有閒錢就揾老師啦<br />\n部琴買番嚟 畢竟係新手<br />\n一星期揾一日出去租琴房摸下真琴熟悉下就得</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都叫有朋友可以教下我 所以又唔算完全自學既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽講yamaha係有少少伏<br />\n不過唔該你"},{"pid":"a3502c1189961339117f2e367665353abdb68549","tid":39528,"uid":27583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T16:15:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>琴行租琴練會唔會好啲</blockquote><br />\n其實租一次可以練幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nthanks bro <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c1a2d50bb792fb85e09678e86bd2ba7d2ec6e29","tid":39528,"uid":38293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T16:36:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>琴行租琴練會唔會好啲</blockquote><br />\n其實租一次可以練幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nthanks bro <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n通常有張叫琴卡嘅嘢 大約$300內 用8-10個鐘"},{"pid":"5afd66d4fc25d7ab702627d1c49131164b86007e","tid":39528,"uid":34429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T16:41:12.000Z","msg":"如果真係認真學就要真琴喇，一開始用電子琴好難改得返手勢<br />\n除非啲電子琴鍵質素好啦，以前有人提過下配備Fater TP40 嘅琴鍵手感唔錯"},{"pid":"ed183145558177841f5bac